1. On-Premises     
Sab kuch customer ko manage karna padta hai:   Hardware, Network,OS, Security, Apps,Data

Yani pura control aur puri responsibility user ki.

2. IaaS (Infrastructure as a Service)   

Microsoft/Azure manage karta hai:    Physical Host, Physical Network, Physical Datacenter

Customer manage karta hai:           Operating System, Applications, Network Controls, Data, Accounts

Example     =                        Azure VM, AWS EC2


3. PaaS (Platform as a Service)  

Microsoft/Azure manage karta hai:      Operating System, Physical Infrastructure, Runtime Environment

Customer manage karta hai:             Applications,Data, Accounts & Identities

Example:                               Azure App Service



4. SaaS (Software as a Service)

Microsoft/Azure almost sab manage karta hai:         Application, OS, Infrastructure, Network

Customer mainly manage karta hai                     Data , Users/Accounts, Devices

Example:                                             Gmail, Office 365, Dropbox

